               <p>SECOND DAY. FRIDAY, DECEMBER 7.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury - before Mr. Sergeant Arabin.,</p>
               <p>13. 
               <persName id="t18271206-13-defend169" type="defendantName">
