               stealing, on the <rs id="t18271206-13-cd69" type="crimeDate">15th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18271206-13-off68 t18271206-13-cd69"></join>, 9 sovereigns, the monies of 
